Welcomes the reports of the Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights on support systems to ensure community inclusion of persons with disabilities, including as a means of building forward better after the coronavirus disease (COVID‑19) pandemic
A/HRC/52/52. and on good practices of support systems enabling community inclusion of persons with disabilities,
A/HRC/55/34. and calls upon all stakeholders to consider the findings and recommendations made in those reports with a view to implementing them;
